title.narrative: New Zealand's Health Adviser to Samoa; supporting investment to the health sector in Samoa.

description.narrative: New Zealand's Health Adviser to Samoa supports targeted and effective investment to the health sector; primarily through strengthened relationships and supporting a partnership approach to all engagements between New Zealand and the health sector in Samoa. The continuation of the role, following a successful initial six months, reflects New Zealand’s ongoing commitment to support Samoa’s vision of “a healthy Samoa”, and recognises how important, and complex, health programming is in Samoa.
